### setting up @uqbar/wallet-ui with vite

Add buffer with node polyfills
yarn add buffer / npm install buffer
for typescript you might need npm install -D @types/node
```
import nodePolyfills from 'vite-plugin-node-stdlib-browser'
// import { Buffer } from "buffer";
// globalThis.Buffer = Buffer;
```
This builds some of the dependencies correctly
```
return defineConfig({
    plugins: [urbitPlugin({ base: 'your-app', target: SHIP_URL, secure: false }), 
	reactRefresh(), 
	nodePolyfills()],
    optimizeDeps: { esbuildOptions: { target: 'es2020'} },
    define: { "process.env.REACT_APP_MOCK_DATA": "true"}, // temp solution for mock-data
  });
  ```


